  Locus:
    Page: 1013
Tags:
  - Invocation=The Dispeller of Sin
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Contemptus Mundi
By: Pythagoras
---
Despise all those things, which when liberated from the body you will not
want; and exercising yourself in those things of which when liberated from
the body you will be in want, invoke the Gods to become your helpers.
